        OOComment:
          'The overall structure of the study follows a logical academic format. However, transitions between sections could be smoother to improve coherence. Some areas particularly the literature review and methodology, would benefit from clearer connections to the research questions and objectives. Additionally, repeated references to concepts like quantitative data or pragmatism need better integration and explanation to maintain clarity and consistency throughout the paper.',
